{
  "texts": [
    "It was also found interesting that the assessments in the lesson plans were mainly quizbased.",
    "The chatbots may produce these behaviorist assessment types since they are more clear and objective ways to measure learning.",
    "However, portfolios or other constructive assessment types were not created for the lesson plans.",
    "As it was described before, ChatGPT was found successful in most quiz-based exams (Choi et al., 2023; Kung et al., 2023; Malinka et al., 2023).",
    "Thus, suggesting a quiz can be a dilemma for chatbot-based learning environments, and, therefore, assessments need to be changed (Rudolph et al., 2023)."
  ]
}